column5:
Rank 1 in open-set image classification task of Open World Vision
  Challenge @ CVPR 2021; The source code and models are publicly available at:
  \url{https://github.com/JDAI-CV/CoTNet}

23 pages, 20 figures, 1 table. v2: corrected typos and minor errors;
  published in ApJ, see the link https://doi.org/10.3847/1538-4357/ac133c
  (there is a misunderstanding for the journal in v1)
